thread.title: Embassy staff and children leave Russian embassy in London

title: Embassy staff and children leave Russian embassy in London
text:
Embassy staff and children leave Russian embassy in London 9:00am EDT - 00:40 
Staff and their families were seen leaving the Russian embassy in London on Tuesday, days after UK Prime Minister Theresa May expelled 23 diplomats following a toxin attack in Salisbury. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
